entry.string: No test patterns selected, will run all tests

docker run --rm \ -v /d/ts-playwright:/app \ -w /app \ -e TEST_USER=${TEST_USER} \ -e TEST_PASSWORD=${TEST_PASSWORD} \ -e BASE_URL=${BASE_URL} \ -e API_KEY=${API_KEY} \ playwright-tests \ npx playwright test tests/api --config=api.config.ts --grep ""

docker run --rm \ -v /d/ts-playwright:/app \ -v /var/jenkins_home/workspace/Playwright-Tests:/workspace \ -w /app \ playwright-tests \ sh -c "cp -r playwright-report /workspace/ 2>/dev/null || true; cp -r test-results /workspace/ 2>/dev/null || true"
